issue.body:
TO-DO:
-Automatic code generation exception handlers after JNI calls.

issue.title: Multiple tests with deploy() lead to errors when loading the native library
issue.body: When running the integration tests, if more than one test deploys the SparkJNI (deploy()), there is undefined behavior in the native code leading to crashes.

issue.title: User-initialized C++ references return NULL to Java
issue.body: In the native-defined C++ object that creates a Java object to be returned to the JVM, env-NewObject(..) returns NULL.
